0.6.0.name: wordpress/commenters-info
0.6.0.description:
The aggregate information and list the commenter.

Localization

"Commenters Info" has been translated into languages. Our thanks and appreciation must go to the following for their contributions:

  • Japanese (ja) - OKAMOTO Wataru (plugin author)
  • Dutch (nl_NL) - Rene
  • German (de_DE) - Rian Klijn
  • Turkish (tr_TR) - Hakan Demiray
  • Russian (ru_RU) - Max Lozovsky
  • Romanian (ro_RO) - Web Geek Sciense

If you have translated into your language, please let me know.
